    "description": {
      "zh": ".300win mag（7.62x67B）规格的穿甲弹，在药筒上置入了一颗220格令Sierra Matchking弹头。该弹药被设计用于击穿中级（及以上）防弹装甲，甚至可威胁部分轻型装甲车辆。由于其硬化弹芯与硬被甲的特性，此弹药极易在各类表面产生跳弹。",
      "en": "A .300 Winchester Magnum (7.62x67B) AP cartridge with a 220-grain Sierra MatchKing bullet. This cartridge was designed to penetrate intermediate (and greater) ballistic armor all the way up to some lightly armored vehicles. Due to it's hardened core and hard jacket, this round is highly likely to bounce off of various surfaces."
    },
